name: Social Media Glassmorphism
description:
Social Media Icon Glass Pack released! 🤩🥳


What is Icon Glass Pack?

This contains 8 customizable and changeable glass icons that have been released for free! 😁😀


This pack's capabilities and features


1 This pack is completely configurable, and you have complete control over everything!


2 This set comes in a variety of colors and styles that you can rapidly choose between!


One of the distinctive features of this collection is the ability to swap between icons with just one click


3 You may use this pack in Dark Mode theme.
